Package org.infinispan.query.logging

Interface Log

All Superinterfaces:
org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
@MessageLogger(projectCode="ISPN") public interface Log extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
Log abstraction for the query module. For this module, message ids ranging from 14001 to 14500 inclusively have been reserved.
Since:
5.0
